products.description: The GMT-Master II ref. 126710BLRO features a 40mm Oystersteel topped with a blue and red Cerachrom bezel.
The Aquanaut ref. 5167A offers a young, modern, and unexpected design with a rubber strap and stainless steel case.
Panerai Submersible watches are built for deep dives, with advanced water resistance and a rugged design.
